                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2476" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0331</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8854 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全球价值链：照亮利丰集团海外并购之路的一盏明灯</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Case Study: Overseas merging and integration of Li &amp;amp; Fung Limited ——Based on Global Supply Chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈建林，薛馨等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利丰公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利丰集团；海外并购；全球价值链；一带一路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Li &amp;amp; Fung Limited; Overseas; Merging and integration; global value chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例是一个描述性案例。随着经济全球一体化迅猛发展和科学技术高速发展，越来越多中国企业趋向于“走出去”，以形成经济全球化条件下参与国际经济合作和竞争的新优势。外面的世界很精彩，外面的世界也很无奈。中国企业掀起了一股海外并购的热潮，然而却并非想象中的一帆风顺。全球约70%的并购没有实现期望的目标与商业价值，足以见得并购整合的困难。海外并购已然成为中国企业提升其国际竞争力的必经之路。但是，企业如何在全球范围内形成其国际竞争力？海外并购通过怎样的整合管理实现期望的目标？这是并购后的企业普遍面临的 “难题”。案例回顾了利丰集团传承三代，历经百年，不断经历着改革与创新，从一个简单的采购代理演变到一个全球性的供应链管理者的角色，并且在当今多变的外部环境中不断地完善，改进并增强和扩充其供应链，形成了当今世界消费品领域独特的核心竞争优势。通过结合全球价值链理论，总结利丰集团的跨国并购成功经验，给正在或者即将走向国际化的外贸企业提供一点思考和启发，尤其是对如何抓住“一带一路”战略的发展机遇，提出重要的借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case is a descriptive case. With the rapid development of economic globalization, science and technology, more and more Chinese companies tend to &quot;go out&quot; to participate in the formation of new advantages under conditions of economic globalization in international economic cooperation and competition. The outside world is very exciting, but also very helpless. Chinese companies set off a wave of overseas M &amp; A boom, but it has not smooth as they think. About 70% of overseas mergers and acquisitions do not achieve the desired objectives and business value, enough to appear the difficulty of merger integration. Overseas M &amp; A has become the must for Chinese enterprises to improve their international competitiveness. However, how to form its international competitiveness over the world? How to achieve the desired goal? This is the post-merger generally faced difficulties. This case look back forward Li &amp; Fung Group, which witnessed the tradition of three generations over one hundred years, constantly undergoing reform and innovation, becoming into the role of a global supply chain manager from a simple purchasing agents evolve and in today&#39;s dynamic external environment, Li&amp; Fung Group continues to improve, enhance and expand its supply chain so that it forms the world&#39;s consumer goods unique core competitive advantage. By combining global value chain theory, from summarizing Li &amp; Fung Group’s successful experience of overseas mergers and acquisitions, this case aims at offering a little thought and inspiration, especially on how to seize opportunities for development &quot;along the way&quot; strategy proposed before.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业资本运作》、《公司理财》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">价值链治理、企业并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
